Apr 7 2004	Loved the staff and excellent service	I love the hotel. The General Manager was extremely nice, so were all the hotel staff members. I had complementery breakfasts every morning (priority club), and complementery fruit baskets every week for staying there. The gym is pretty good, however, the equipment tended to break down, though the management would fix it quickly. The location isn't the best, but the Orpheum theatre is close by, so people walk around all the time. The hotel is also really close to the BART Civic Center station, which is very convenient for anyone who would like to travel via BART.I would recommend this hotel to anyone visiting SF.	
